CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 5, 1959, pg. 7, reads: "Annual Affair Thoroughly Enjoyed by Youngsters - Courier Newsboys Play, Eat, Win Prizes at Picnic -Happy Pie-eating Contest Winners"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four adolescent boys, two wearing striped shirt, holding pie stained plates, seated on picnic  table at South Park during Pittsburgh Courier Newsboy Picnic
